29.0: {"post_id": "https://www.instagram.com/p/CGy2oeGgCH5/", "op": "https://www.instagram.com/uwchisigs/", "caption": "uwchisigs \ud835\ude34\ud835\ude26\ud835\ude2d\ud835\ude27 \ud835\ude2d\ud835\ude30\ud835\ude37\ud835\ude26 \ud835\ude34\ud835\ude36\ud835\ude2f\ud835\ude25\ud835\ude22\ud835\ude3a\u2063 \u2063 \u201cself-love to me is seeing yourself as a best friend you care about. with best friends you hype them up, you have deep conversations, you give them grace, you spend time and try new things with them, and you\u2019re able to be yourself around them. self-love is being able to do all those things for yourself.  how i practice self love is i dance my heart out. and i think to myself \u201cyou\u2019re a fun person to be around sheila\u201d. i also discover more about self-love as i journal. i write down what i\u2019m feeling, i answer questions that i have for myself, i write down my hopes, dreams, values, etc. a stream of consciousness written down, so that when i reread i can visualize more clearly what\u2019s being kept inside myself.\u201d \u2063 #chisigs #uwchisigs #chisigmaalpha #uwchisigmaalpha #selflovesunday 11h", "num_likes": 86, "num_hashtags": 5, "hashtags": ["https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/chisigs/", "https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/uwchisigs/", "https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/chisigmaalpha/", "https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/uwchisigmaalpha/", "https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/selflovesunday/"], "location": "", "date": 1603688400.0, "lat": "", "lon": ""}
